                        Sell
                    </h4>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <ul>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">Who can sell on eZeelo?</li>
                        <li>eZeelo provides an opportunity to the local traditional retailers, wholesalers, service providers of the city to make a very comprehensive and viable presence in the fast growing ecommerce segment by partnering on a win-win proposition. </li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">How do I sell on eZeelo?</li>
                        <li>
                            Merchant who wish to partner with us, can log on to merchant.ezeelo.com  and register themselves.
                            <br />Merchants can contact our customer care +91-9860890890.
                        </li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">When can I start selling?</li>
                        <li>Once the e-shop of merchants are created and hosted on the portal, products are ready-to-be-sold.</li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">Where all I can sell my products?</li>
                        <li>Merchants products are showcased to thousands of buyers across India through our hassle-free processes and team of professionals.</li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">What is my reach across India?</li>
                        <li>eZeelo is the online mega-store having a localized presence in Lucknow and Kanpur offering a wide range of products like Fruits, Fresh Vegetables, Exotic Fruits and Vegetables, Groceries, Electronics, Home Décor, Fashion, Lifestyle, Electricals, Lightings etc. at the most competitive prices from local stores. eZeelo is empowering the local merchants, retailers and vendors to sell their products and services and a range of more than 50000+ products are listed. eZeelo is your one-stop online marketplace where you name the product, and you get it.</li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">What about promotions and advertising?</li>
                        <li>
                            In order to help the retailers to promote their establishments among the genuine and targeted customers, promotion of Retail Establishment are done via:<br />
                            a) Banner ads.<br />
                            b) Ads per Click including Facebook promotions, digital marketing, Offline Co-branding and Promotion.<br />
                            Continuous promotion of retailers via portal among target audience will ensure large number of visitors to the market place.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
