            <div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <ul>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">Who decides the price of the product?</li>
                        <li>Merchant will decide the price of their product.</li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">What are the fees charged?</li>
                        <li>For fees and other related further queries, please contact our customer care +91-9860890890.</li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">What is Commission fee and how much commission is charged?</li>
                        <li>Commission rate is based on the plans registered with. For further queries, please contact our customer care +91-9860890890.</li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">How and when do I get paid?</li>
                        <li>Merchant settlements are done weekly. For further details, please contact our customer care +91-9860890890.</li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">What is the procedure for payment settlement?</li>
                        <li>Merchant payments are settled over a 7 day payment cycle period after successful completion of delivery by logistics team and submission of requisite documents.</li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">What is the duration for payment settlement?</li>
                        <li>For all orders from Sunday to Saturday to be settled every week on Wednesdays.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
