                <div class="panel-body">
                    <ul>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">How do I manage my orders on eZeelo?</li>
                        <li>You are provided with a separate merchant portal to maintain your order & track delivery (link- <a href="http://merchant.ezeelo.com/" target="_blank" style="color:blue;">merchant.ezeelo.com</a>). </li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">Do I need to courier my products to eZeelo?</li>
                        <li>We provide pick-up service of orders along with home delivery service through our in house logistic team. There is no need to courier products by merchants.</li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">Does eZeelo provide packaging material?</li>
                        <li>No, eZeelo does not provide packaging material to merchants.</li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">How are you going to do pick up for the products?</li>
                        <li>Our pickup partner will pick the products from your given address with required details & delivered the products to the customer. </li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">How are you going to deliver the products?</li>
                        <li>
                            Products pick-up takes place as per designated time.<br />
                            Products packaging takes place accordingly & delivered.
                        </li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">Who takes care of the delivery of my products?</li>
                        <li>eZeelo has its own in-house logistics teams who ensures timely order pick-up and delivery services of the products from merchants to customers.</li>
                        <li style=" font-weight: bold;">What should I do if my area is not serviceable by eZeelo?</li>
                        <li>Merchant support required for product pick up.<br />Merchants can opt to stock their merchandise with us.</li>
                    </ul>
